      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 14:40:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚马逊因黑客攻击暂停推出 Microsoft Office 一年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/amazon-paused-rollout-of-microsoft-office-for-a-year-after-hacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊公司已将微软公司基于云端的 Office 套件的部署推迟了一年，两家公司正努力解决亚马逊对电子邮件和生产力软件包安全性的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/amazon-paused-rollout-of-microsoft-office-for-a-year-after-hacks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 14:37:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
